{"article_id":"vzzRIuhM06EGAUjE","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"On Capitol Hill today , a no show .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"At the request of President Trump , former White House attorney Don McGahn is defying a subpoena","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"to testify before Congress about the Russia investigation .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"McGahn was a key witness in Robert Mueller 's report ,","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"and Democrats believe","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"he offered the most damaging evidence against the president .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"White House Counsel Pat Cipollone says","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"McGahn should not testify","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"due to `` constitutional immunity ''","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"and `` in order to protect the prerogatives of the Office of the Presidency . ''","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"Backing that up ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"the Justice Department issued an opinion","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"saying ,","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"`` Congress may not constitutionally compel the president 's senior advisers to testify about their official duties . ''","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"`` At the end of that he said","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"there 's no collusion .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"Now what happens ?","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"The Democrats want a redo","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"and we 've had enough","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"and the country has had enough , ''","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"he told reporters on the south lawn of the White House","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"before boarding Marine One for a campaign rally in Pennsylvania .","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"`` We have a president","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"that is actively trying to cover up","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"and prevent the American people from getting to the truth ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"and that is not something","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"I think","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"we can not tolerate , ''","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"says Rep. David Cicilline","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"( D-RI ) .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"Now demands for impeachment among Democrats are growing louder .","depth":4},{"id":32,"text":"A number of leaders Monday night privately pressed Speaker of the House of Representatives Nancy Pelosi to allow the hearings","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"to help Democrats attain the documents and testimony","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"they 're seeking","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"without interference from the White House .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"Speaker Pelosi has consistently rejected the idea ,","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"but House Judiciary Committee Chairman Jerrold Nadler","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"( D-NY )","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"says","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"the president is n't above the law .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"`` The recalcitrance of the president and his lawless behavior is making it more and more difficult to ignore all options","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"including impeachment , ''","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"Rep. Nadler said on CNN on Monday .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Democrats","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"calling for impeachment","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"have found a friend in Republican Congressman Justin Amash","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"( R-MI ) .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"`` I think","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"it 's a process","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"and it 's something","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"that should be begun , ''","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Rep. Amash told reporters","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"as he left the Capitol Monday .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"`` He 's been a loser for a long time .","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"Rarely votes for Republicans","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"and personally I think","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"he 's not much , ''","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"he said .","depth":5},{"id":59,"text":"However , a federal judge handed Democrats a victory Monday ,","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"upholding a congressional subpoena for the president 's financial records from an accounting firm .","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"The judge 's opinion also states","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"that Congress can investigate the president 's conduct both before and after he took office .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"`` It is simply not fathomable that a constitution","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"that grants Congress the power","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"to remove a president for reasons","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"including criminal behavior","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"would deny Congress the power","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"to investigate him for unlawful conduct past or present","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"even without formally opening an impeachment inquiry , ''","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"US District Court Judge Amit Metha wrote .","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"Using history as her guide ,","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"Pelosi fears","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"impeachment proceedings against the president would be unpopular ,","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"as they were against President Bill Clinton ,","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"causing voters to rally to Trump 's defense in 2020 .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":151,"left":0,"right":150,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":150,"left":118,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":105,"right":117,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":97,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":1,"right":96,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":96,"left":80,"right":95,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":80,"left":77,"right":79,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":4,"right":78,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity